title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report. Steps to reproduce: 1. Export the data in the table. Expected result: The data should be exported successfully. Actual result: An exception is encountered in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
OB: The data should be exported successfully.
EB: An exception is encountered in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method when attempting to export the data from the table.
SR: Investigate the cause of the exception in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method and fix the issue to allow for successful data export from the table.
